{"tid":215422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔣麗芸：有冇考慮訓練吓啲流浪貓捉老鼠呀？","createTime":"2017-04-24T11:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T12:51:53.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9bba19d9a4741d3a7710a014e7f5aa093f9a455a","tid":215422,"uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T11:55:19.000Z","msg":"立法會今召開研究動物權益相關事宜小組委員會會議，商討政府處理流浪動物方面的工作。漁護署在2015年1月接納愛護動物協會及保護遺棄動物協會建議，在長洲及元朗大棠試驗為期3年的「捕捉、絕育、放回」（TNR）計劃，為捕獲的流浪狗絕育，再放回原居地，以新方式控制流浪狗數目。計劃推行至今2年，署方指現階段作出結論為時尚早，認為仍有待取得更多數據，方可進一步評估計劃的成效。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯陳克勤及民主黨鄺俊宇提問，政府會否計劃擴大試驗試劃，於更多地區實施。食衛局副局長陳肇始回應指，對此局方持開放態度，並認為要先累積實驗計劃的經驗，進一步評估計劃，亦需要與各區進行溝通。<br />\n公民黨譚文豪提出，政府是否考慮開放動物中心，讓市民可於中心內直接領養動物。漁護署助理署長薛漢宗稱，領養中心需另尋覓地方及增加人手作處理，需要時間作長遠計劃。<br />\n當局回應小組主席蔣麗芸時指，去年一共捕捉及接收約800隻流浪猫。蔣麗芸隨即表示，「有冇考慮訓練吓啲流浪貓捉老鼠呀？」她笑言捕捉老鼠為猫之天性，「可以諗諗去訓練佢哋！」"},{"pid":"fcd324fb81264b498de7ada5eb3b6991abe6f005","tid":215422,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"訓練左蔣議員識用個腦先啦"},{"pid":"70ca776de73983826f437c1977f3ea4fe6dcb823","tid":215422,"uid":51594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:02:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓練左蔣議員識用個腦先啦</blockquote><br />\n練嚟都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024662a617153dd559f925a394c8137604effced","tid":215422,"uid":49643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:02:58.000Z","msg":"駛唔駛訓練埋d流浪漢做保安？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bde82c8cf59c0a55d10fb4dd3963dcf2c00cecd","tid":215422,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:08:03.000Z","msg":"可唔可以訓練警犬幫你捉返個腦"},{"pid":"2f35ad0d4be25d656694d82deb2fd8a3566efaa6","tid":215422,"uid":5283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:13:27.000Z","msg":"流浪貓都要增值"},{"pid":"519a3aa8accd2ebe5115c8b34806fcfb50347a54","tid":215422,"uid":42536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:23:37.000Z","msg":"訓練流浪犬做警犬吖笨"},{"pid":"e2fc4d3a40b78cf08a78d9718a9567791296d70f","tid":215422,"uid":9736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:26:06.000Z","msg":"訓練古惑仔做律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30cf6beb1b99ac1170d7cfa6101552092a7d147","tid":215422,"uid":13149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:33:27.000Z","msg":"咁不如訓練埋流浪貓坐你個位丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37ff0455f413ba8fe7f7f4b2a9c6193cb0897f7","tid":215422,"uid":92315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:42:47.000Z","msg":"你唔好話訓練叮噹唔驚老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c022974a03be9a27c7f1028645741aab31bf7187","tid":215422,"uid":28767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:45:20.000Z","msg":"到底有冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09a7ada4d74f4e9bf241762cccd2f586a95f5e9","tid":215422,"uid":110699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:50:15.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0116a67cb68d6a1e3ce1c5bebb163bf4f94add5","tid":215422,"uid":12991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"喂你求其訓練一隻黎睇下先好無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}